data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! NICE PRICE REDUCTION! WELCOME TO THIS BEAUTIFUL POOL HOME IN DESIRABLE LAKE MARIAM HILLS, A GATED COMMUNITY LOCATED IN SE WINTER HAVEN, THIS CHARMING HOUSE OFFERS AN EXCEPTIONAL LIVING EXPERIENCE!!   MOVE IN READY! 4 BEDROOMS WITH A BEAUTIFUL MASTER ROOM WITH DUAL SINKS, JETTED GARDEN TUB, TILE SHOWER & LARGE WALK IN CLOSET WITH BUILT-IN ORGANIZERS (ALL OTHER BEDROOM'S HAS A CLOSETS ARE UPGRADED WITH THE BUILT-IN ORGANIZERS).ONE ROOM INCLUDES A BUILT-IN HOME OFFICE SPACE.  ENJOY THE PEACEFUL POOL AREA SURROUNDED BY BEAUTIFUL BUTTERFLIES. SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM WITH GAS FIREPLACE, CROWN MOLDING, AND CERAMIC TILE FLOORS. HIGH CEILINGS & RECESSED LIGHTING IN EAT-IN KITCHEN WITH STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES & WALK-IN PANTRY. FRENCH DOORS LEAD TO SCREEN ENCLOSED POOL AREA.   THIS GATED COMMUNITY FEATURES LIGHTED STREETS WITH PRIVATE BOAT RAMP WITH ACCESS TO LAKE MARIAM. CONVENIENT TO LEGOLAND, BUSCH GARDENS, AND ABOUT 45 MINUTES FROM THE BEACHES AND DISNEY AREA.   DON’T MISS THE OPPORTUNITY TO CALL THIS EXTRAORDINARY PROPERTY YOURS AND ELEVATE YOUR FLORIDA LIVING EXPERIENCE!
